org.wattdepot.common.util.csv

Class CSVObjectFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wattdepot.common.util.csv.CSVObjectFactory

  • public class CSVObjectFactory
extends Object
    ObjectFactory factory class for converting WattDepot domain model instances into a CSV entry and converting a CSV entry into a domain model instance.

    Cam Moore
